
  * items 横排时自动等高 container
  * items 竖排时自动等宽 container
  * items 根据 content 调节宽度
  * items 随 axis 方向有 左到右，右到左，上到下，下到上 4种变化
  * 可以跟 break point 结合


  flex items 对齐 container flex axis 的起始位置

    .justify-content-start
    .justify-content-sm-start
    .justify-content-md-start
    .justify-content-lg-start
    .justify-content-xl-start

    http://codepen.io/HarryWang74/pen/NjPobK


  flex items 对齐 container flex axis 的终止位置

    .justify-content-end
    .justify-content-sm-end
    .justify-content-md-end
    .justify-content-lg-end
    .justify-content-xl-end

    http://codepen.io/HarryWang74/pen/oWgmoy



  flex items 对齐 container flex axis 的中间

    .justify-content-center
    .justify-content-sm-center
    .justify-content-md-center
    .justify-content-lg-center
    .justify-content-xl-center

    http://codepen.io/HarryWang74/pen/WjbPPx



  items 横向撑满 container, 两边留空，中间等分
    只有在 items 宽度总和小于 container 宽度，两边才有留空
    当 items 宽度总和大于 container 宽度，items 自动撑满 container，两边没有留空

    .justify-content-around
    .justify-content-sm-around
    .justify-content-md-around
    .justify-content-lg-around
    .justify-content-xl-around

    http://codepen.io/HarryWang74/pen/ybyZWX


  items 横向撑满 container，两边不留空，中间等分

    .justify-content-between
    .justify-content-sm-between
    .justify-content-md-between
    .justify-content-lg-between
    .justify-content-xl-between

    http://codepen.io/HarryWang74/pen/oWgmrJ
